room_title: Escape room "Tiki Time!" by 60out Escape Rooms in Los Angeles
room_address: 2284 S Figueroa St Los Angeles, CA 90007
room_description: Welcome to the islands! You’ve traveled to the home of your ancestors, a tropical paradise. Why would you ever want to escape? You wouldn’t! Tiki Time is the first game where your goal is to stay in as long as possible by solving challenges to add time to your visit. Can your team earn enough time for you to complete your tasks and pay tribute at the shrine of the island king?
